title: Flo Mounier Extreme Metal Drumming 101 DVD Rip
description:
This is a rip of all of the video files from both disks of the original DVD.
I even took the time to number everything in the order it was in on the DVD and take screen shots of the menus so you can read all the little tips from those as well. All in all it's a pretty good alternative to the 7.9GB full DVD copy that's floating around.

Note that Disk 1 is the instructional part and Disk 2 is mostly just drum solos. You only need to download what you want!
